# Engine state directory (forge artifact placeholder).
#
# silence-window.json is created at runtime by engine.sh state_ensure()
# under ~/.gawd/fallbacks/state/silence-window.json on a deployed Gawd.
# This directory exists in the forge artifact so the install layout is
# explicit; the runtime location is determined by GAWD_FALLBACK_STATE_DIR
# (default ~/.gawd/fallbacks/state/).
